"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?21/51/22325/abstract/5\">",
"      Dostert A, Heinzel T. Negative glucocorticoid receptor response elements and their role in glucocorticoid action. Curr Pharm Des 2004; 10:2807.",
"     </a>",
